Text: That's not Rihanna, it's a beached whale.  Or maybe a pregnant walrus.  Whatever, it's HUGE and ugly.

The last time a whale was beached on the shores of Honolulu, a rather dark and shady individual began to fuck its blow hole. Greenpeace had to intervene.

Is it a coincidence that our dear uploader seems to have miscategorized his "hot" pictures?
